    "millsfield:images_texts": [
      "SYSTEM TIMETABLE\nEffective April 2, 1995\nAMERICAN TRANS AIR\nTAA\nOn ATA You're On Vacation ™",
      "Easy\nDoes It.\nWelcome to ATA Amber\nVacations. Great vacation\npackages that are easy to\nput together and very easy\non your wallet. Our pack-\nages combine the best of\nthe vacation destinations\nyou want with prices you'll\nlove.\nOne phone call is all it\ntakes to pick your ATA\nflight, hotel, and ground\ntransportation. And you'll\npay less because of our\ngreat buying power. There's\nno easier way mentally or\neconomically to get the\nbest vacation package to\nFlorida, the Caribbean,\nMexico, Phoenix, Las\nVegas, California or Hawaii.\nAMBER VACATIONS\nMake it easy on yourself.\nCall your travel agent or\n800-442-8952."
    ],
